text:
Flushing Bay (Queens): Viewing northeast across the bay, showing College Point in the background. The vantage point for these views is Ditmars Boulevard at about 31st Avenue.

P. L. Sperr

View 1: June 8, 1927
View 2: Oct. 4, 1935
title: Flushing Bay - Queens - [College Point.]
